"Funzioni evento valide: GetPosition, GetRange."

#: wxcrafter/controls/rich_text_ctrl_wrapper.cpp:55
msgid ""
"Process a wxEVT_COMMAND_RICHTEXT_CONTENT_DELETED event, generated when content has been deleted from the control\n"
